App description: This app will allow each user to find other user with related goals/tasks with the purpose of allowing these users to provide motivation to one another.

User Stories:

Users create accounts, with the option of attaching an email to their account.

Users can search for groups by category or by keyword.

Anyone can create a group and allow people into their group

Group members share related goals with one another.

Each group has a group chat.

There is a calendar for keeping track of goals and group events.
